        <V n="text" t="single">
          <T n="single">0xD08312E2<!--String: "When I was growing up, I felt alone a lot. My brother had close friends and was always off with them and, if he included me, it was probably just out of pity. As in, I bet our mom made him do that. Mom used to tell me that someday I would find another Sim who would understand me the way that I am.\n\nWell, she was right. I did find another Sim like that. Or at least, I thought they were like that. But they don't care about me the way I wanted them to, and I feel even worse now. They told me the Sim they really loved was someone more social and cheerful than I am.\n\nSometimes I feel like being alone all the time would be easier than trying to open up to another Sim only to have them make me feel this sad and empty."--></T>
